{"type":"text","timestamp":1775820572341,"sessionID":"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I","part":{"id":"prt_d77276eed001d2Jem7yW0jVfhB","messageID":"msg_d772764f70017FgYS1HFLgCfQN","sessionID":"ses_288db7c39ffeZ1l0ExGm1Z4v9I","type":"text","text":"Written `changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md` with 15 requirements and 60+ acceptance scenarios covering:\n\n- **SandboxReconciler** struct & dependency injection\n- **Workqueue** rate limiting (exponential backoff: 5s initial, 5min max, 15 retries)\n- **Informer registration** with event callbacks (Add/Update/Delete for AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, Pod)\n- **Reconciler startup** with cache sync (30s timeout)\n- **AgentRuntime reconciliation** — OnAdd (CR creation → StoreSandbox), OnUpdate (status mapping → UpdateSandbox), OnDelete (Store cleanup)\n- **CodeInterpreter reconciliation** — same pattern + Warm Pool event handling\n- **Pod status listener** — IP/EntryPoints update on Running state change\n- **Reconciliation key design** — `namespace/name` via `MetaNamespaceKeyFunc`\n- **Status mapping** — K8s `Ready` condition → Store status (pending/running/terminated)\n- **Graceful shutdown** — informer stop → queue drain (30s) → store close\n- **Error handling** — retryable vs non-recoverable errors\n- **Prometheus metrics** — reconcile total/duration/errors, workqueue depth/adds\n- **Handler integration** — optional reconciler reference in create/delete handlers\n- **End-to-end ordering** — full reconcile loop sequence\n- **Build & test gates** — compile, test, coverage ≥80%, T/C >0.4, no race conditions","time":{"start":1775820572339,"end":1775820572339}}}
